1
00:00:12,125 --> 00:00:15,041
Lokasi terakhir formasi sihir
ialah Plaza Tasik Emas.

2
00:00:16,166 --> 00:00:18,833
Kisah ini pasti jadi
tajuk utama berita esok.

3
00:00:27,458 --> 00:00:29,500
PLAZA TASIK EMAS

4
00:00:29,583 --> 00:00:31,250
KAMERA 1

5
00:00:33,375 --> 00:00:34,541
Celaka Wu Tien-chi.

6
00:00:41,875 --> 00:00:45,125
Yu-ching, ayah datang.

7
00:00:45,833 --> 00:00:46,750
Wang Cheng-nan!

8
00:00:48,916 --> 00:00:51,375
Pergi! Jangan dekati saya.

9
00:00:51,458 --> 00:00:52,291
Okey.

10
00:00:52,375 --> 00:00:54,791
- Jangan dekati saya.
- Bertenang.

11
00:00:54,875 --> 00:00:57,166
Jangan terburu-buru. Turun dulu.

12
00:00:57,250 --> 00:00:59,666
Saya dah muak dengan dunia yang keji ini.

13
00:00:59,750 --> 00:01:02,041
Polis pun sama saja.

14
00:01:03,166 --> 00:01:05,375
Jika saya terjun,

15
00:01:05,458 --> 00:01:09,125
barulah kisah saya tular
dan polis ambil serius.

16
00:01:09,208 --> 00:01:11,958
Polis belum sahkan
itu mayat Wang Yu-ching.

17
00:01:12,041 --> 00:01:15,000
Kita akan jumpa pelakunya nanti.
Masih ada harapan.

18
00:01:15,541 --> 00:01:17,791
- Turun dulu.
- Jangan dekati saya.

19
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:21,041
Saya dah bunuh orang.

20
00:01:21,125 --> 00:01:23,041
Saya dah bunuh anak haram itu.

21
00:01:23,625 --> 00:01:25,208
Chao, En. Wang nak terjun.

22
00:01:25,291 --> 00:01:28,041
Ujian DNA sahkan
itu bukan mayat Wang Yu-ching.

23
00:01:28,125 --> 00:01:31,083
Kita baru dapat maklumat.
Halang En. Wang sekarang!

24
00:01:31,166 --> 00:01:33,083
Sial kau, Wu Tien-chi.

25
00:01:33,166 --> 00:01:36,250
Dia di hospital dan tak mati.
Awak tak bunuh sesiapa.

26
00:01:36,333 --> 00:01:38,041
Janganlah buat benda bodoh.

27
00:01:38,125 --> 00:01:41,375
Kamu semua tipu saya.

28
00:01:42,208 --> 00:01:43,625
Anak saya dah mati.

29
00:01:44,125 --> 00:01:45,541
Saya bunuh orang.

30
00:01:45,625 --> 00:01:48,333
- Semuanya dah terlambat.
- Wang Cheng-nan!

31
00:01:58,500 --> 00:02:00,416
Saya pun pernah cuba bunuh diri.

32
00:02:03,208 --> 00:02:04,833
Saya nak semuanya berakhir.

33
00:02:08,458 --> 00:02:09,750
Tapi percayalah.

34
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:14,416
Awak akan menyesal selepas mati.

35
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:17,833
Betul.

36
00:02:22,041 --> 00:02:26,750
Fikirkan anak awak.
Apa dia nak buat kalau awak mati?

37
00:02:30,708 --> 00:02:32,125
- Yu-ching.
- Turunlah.

38
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:38,750
Tunggu!

39
00:02:38,833 --> 00:02:40,083
Anak awak hidup lagi!

40
00:02:40,166 --> 00:02:42,291
Ujian DNA sahkan itu bukan mayat dia.

41
00:02:43,291 --> 00:02:44,125
Jangan terjun.

42
00:02:48,708 --> 00:02:49,750
Hei!

43
00:03:00,166 --> 00:03:02,958
KAMERA 1

44
00:03:16,916 --> 00:03:21,916
AGENT FROM ABOVE

45
00:03:22,958 --> 00:03:26,958
KETIBAAN

46
00:03:50,750 --> 00:03:53,500
- Telefon ambulans!
- Mangsa culik ditemui. Hantar ambulans.

47
00:03:53,583 --> 00:03:56,250
- Semua unit, mangsa ditemui.
- Kosongkan laluan.

48
00:03:56,333 --> 00:03:57,416
Wang Yu-ching.

49
00:03:58,291 --> 00:03:59,250
Wang Yu-ching.

50
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:15,041
Lelaki yang awak tikam itu
tak cedera parah.

51
00:04:15,125 --> 00:04:17,083
Dia dah dipindahkan ke wad biasa.

52
00:04:21,708 --> 00:04:23,416
Hei. Lap tangan.

53
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,125
Yu-ching.

54
00:05:00,916 --> 00:05:03,250
Jangan takut.

55
00:05:24,875 --> 00:05:26,000
Tunggu sekejap.

56
00:05:28,958 --> 00:05:30,583
Nah. Bawa ini sekali.

57
00:05:34,083 --> 00:05:35,291
- Kak Lo.
- Ya?

58
00:05:35,375 --> 00:05:37,333
Betulkah awak tak nak pergi?

59
00:05:38,041 --> 00:05:40,333
Saya nak tinggal sini. Awak pergilah.

60
00:05:40,416 --> 00:05:44,500
Jangan lupa jaga makan, faham?

61
00:05:53,041 --> 00:05:55,833
- Jadi, janganlah rindukan saya.
- Yalah.

62
00:06:34,875 --> 00:06:35,708
Kakak.

63
00:06:42,666 --> 00:06:46,625
Setelah lama menyorok,
akhirnya awak dah sanggup jumpa kakak?

64
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:57,125
Saya tak sanggup jumpa,

65
00:06:57,750 --> 00:07:00,916
sebab saya nak kakak
boleh lupakan saya cepat-cepat.

66
00:07:02,708 --> 00:07:04,375
Saya ingat lama-lama nanti

67
00:07:05,291 --> 00:07:06,791
kakak dapat lupakan saya.

68
00:07:07,708 --> 00:07:11,458
Tapi selepas beberapa tahun,
kakak masih tak boleh lupakan saya.

69
00:07:14,791 --> 00:07:16,083
Janganlah menangis.

70
00:07:16,166 --> 00:07:19,541
Kakak asyik sebut nama saya
setiap pagi macam baca doa.

71
00:07:19,625 --> 00:07:21,125
Siapa yang boleh tahan?

72
00:07:21,208 --> 00:07:24,375
Awak bodohkah?
Takkanlah kakak boleh lupakan awak.

73
00:07:25,875 --> 00:07:27,125
Bodoh betul.

74
00:07:28,875 --> 00:07:30,875
Saya memang tak pandai sangat pun.

75
00:07:39,166 --> 00:07:44,166
Setiap hari saya berdoa kepada dewa
supaya kakak selamat.

76
00:07:44,666 --> 00:07:46,125
Kakak nak saya tenang bersemadi.

77
00:07:46,208 --> 00:07:48,458
Tapi itu mustahil jika kakak tak selamat.

78
00:07:50,041 --> 00:07:53,250
Dengarlah cakap Chieh.
Tinggalkan Pasar Dongfeng cepat.

79
00:07:55,083 --> 00:07:56,500
Habis, awak bagaimana?

80
00:07:56,583 --> 00:07:59,000
Awak tak boleh pergi. Awak roh duniawi.

81
00:07:59,083 --> 00:08:01,416
Saya dan jiran dah lama jadi hantu.

82
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:04,541
Lagipun,
Ejen Putera Mahkota Ketiga jaga kami.

83
00:08:04,625 --> 00:08:06,125
Siapa berani kacau kami?

84
00:08:08,166 --> 00:08:10,666
Jadi, awak akan lawat kakak lagi nanti?

85
00:08:13,208 --> 00:08:14,833
Janji satu perkara dulu.

86
00:08:15,333 --> 00:08:16,166
Janji apa?

87
00:08:19,583 --> 00:08:21,458
Biasakan hidup tanpa saya.

88
00:08:24,958 --> 00:08:27,250
Kemudian teruskanlah hidup kakak.

89
00:08:32,166 --> 00:08:34,083
Jangan terlalu fikirkan saya.

90
00:08:34,583 --> 00:08:35,958
Sekali-sekala saja.

91
00:08:41,541 --> 00:08:42,541
Kalau…

92
00:08:43,583 --> 00:08:45,166
kalau ada rezeki…

93
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:49,291
kita jumpa semula di sini.

94
00:08:58,166 --> 00:08:59,000
Okey.

95
00:09:00,666 --> 00:09:02,125
Kakak pergi esok.

96
00:09:25,458 --> 00:09:27,416
Memang nyaris-nyaris tadi.

97
00:09:28,916 --> 00:09:31,083
Nasib baik kita tarik dia.

98
00:09:35,166 --> 00:09:36,333
Helo.

99
00:09:38,666 --> 00:09:39,500
Ya.

100
00:09:41,333 --> 00:09:42,166
Okey.

101
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:44,291
Okey, faham.

102
00:09:45,250 --> 00:09:46,083
Siallah.

103
00:09:46,166 --> 00:09:47,875
Ada pelabur yang rugi

104
00:09:47,958 --> 00:09:50,833
terjun bangunan
berdekatan lokasi En. Wang tadi.

105
00:09:51,333 --> 00:09:54,125
- Bila masa kematiannya?
- Kira-kira sejam lalu.

106
00:09:55,041 --> 00:09:56,250
Ini gambar si mati.

107
00:09:59,375 --> 00:10:00,708
JANTINA: LELAKI

108
00:10:02,833 --> 00:10:04,125
Lif rosak.

109
00:10:04,833 --> 00:10:06,458
Hidup saya dah berakhirkah?

110
00:10:25,708 --> 00:10:27,708
- Bedebah itu ada pelan B.
- Sial.

111
00:10:27,791 --> 00:10:31,291
Formasi sihir dah sempurna.
Roh Raja Syaitan akan memasuki tubuhnya.

112
00:11:53,708 --> 00:11:58,000
Akhirnya aku berjaya sampai ke sini.

113
00:12:08,625 --> 00:12:10,125
Bulan purnama malam esok.

114
00:12:11,875 --> 00:12:13,458
Pasar Dongfeng jadi medan perang.

115
00:12:15,791 --> 00:12:18,625
Gilalah. Ini dah macam Stranger Things.

116
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,000
Han Chieh.

117
00:13:16,833 --> 00:13:19,666
- Semua orang dah pergi. Kenapa datang?
- Hantu-hantu ada lagi.

118
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:21,916
Saya bawa snek untuk Hsiao-ming dan nenek.

119
00:13:24,041 --> 00:13:26,416
Saya nak ambil senjata
daripada Fu. Baliklah.

120
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,958
Pertarungan itu malam ini, bukan?

121
00:13:33,208 --> 00:13:34,291
Ya.

122
00:13:34,375 --> 00:13:36,916
Boleh saya ikut? Semasa waktu siang saja.

123
00:13:40,416 --> 00:13:42,833
Kaki awak, ikut suka awaklah.

124
00:13:42,916 --> 00:13:45,583
Nanti ada tempat saya nak pergi.
Boleh awak ikut saya?

125
00:14:08,583 --> 00:14:11,083
Selepas jatuh sakit,
kadangkala saya datang

126
00:14:11,166 --> 00:14:14,250
untuk tenangkan fikiran
dan buat hajat di pokok ini.

127
00:14:39,541 --> 00:14:42,875
Saya buat macam ritual.
Saya selalu akhiri dengan doa.

128
00:14:50,333 --> 00:14:51,291
Selesai.

129
00:14:53,291 --> 00:14:56,125
- Apa hajat awak?
- Keamanan dunia.

130
00:15:00,916 --> 00:15:03,875
- Awak yakin ia dimakbulkan?
- Saya yakin.

131
00:15:03,958 --> 00:15:05,333
Pak cik beritahu saya,

132
00:15:05,416 --> 00:15:07,666
"Sihir tak boleh kalahkan kuasa suci,

133
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:11,000
kuasa suci tak boleh kalahkan karma,
karma tak boleh kalahkan hajat."

134
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:15,166
Jadi, orang yang buat hajat
lebih kuat daripada Doktor Strange.

135
00:15:15,791 --> 00:15:18,833
Awak rasa dunia boleh
jadi aman dengan hajat?

136
00:15:20,208 --> 00:15:21,333
Mungkin.

137
00:15:21,833 --> 00:15:25,083
Sebab saya tujukan
kasih sayang saya kepada dunia.

138
00:15:42,458 --> 00:15:43,541
Suka hati awaklah.

139
00:15:44,416 --> 00:15:45,708
Buatlah hajat juga.

140
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:52,833
- Tak nak.
- Satu hajat saja.

141
00:15:53,416 --> 00:15:55,750
Hei, buatlah satu hajat saja.

142
00:15:59,166 --> 00:16:03,291
JABATAN POLIS BANDAR TAIPEI
PRESINT DAERAH TENGAH

143
00:16:16,375 --> 00:16:17,375
Ayuh.

144
00:16:19,916 --> 00:16:21,666
Mari bersiap untuk malam ini.

145
00:16:25,833 --> 00:16:27,583
BATA EMAS

146
00:16:58,291 --> 00:17:00,750
MATILAH KAU, RAJA SYAITAN

147
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:04,416
Han Chieh, adakah ini pasti berkesan?

148
00:17:05,291 --> 00:17:07,166
Kuasa ajaib boleh lawan hantu.

149
00:17:07,833 --> 00:17:10,166
Tolong saya. Banyak yang perlu ditulis.

150
00:17:17,458 --> 00:17:18,333
BENGANG GILA

151
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:39,208
Dah selesai di sana?

152
00:17:42,416 --> 00:17:43,625
DONGFENG PALING KUAT

153
00:17:43,708 --> 00:17:45,708
INI ZON EJEN PUTERA MAHKOTA KETIGA

154
00:17:45,791 --> 00:17:47,416
PUTERA MAHKOTA TAK TERKALAH

155
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:48,958
DONGFENG YANG TERBAIK

156
00:17:49,041 --> 00:17:51,083
CHIEH PASTI MENANG

157
00:17:54,291 --> 00:17:56,000
RAJA SYAITAN DAN WU TIEN-CHI,

158
00:17:56,083 --> 00:17:57,875
MAMPUSLAH KAU!

159
00:18:21,125 --> 00:18:23,666
Alamak. Cukupkah ada lapan saja?

160
00:18:27,541 --> 00:18:28,625
Han Chieh.

161
00:18:32,916 --> 00:18:35,208
Masanya hampir tiba. Awak patut balik.

162
00:18:35,291 --> 00:18:37,125
Apa lagi yang boleh saya bantu?

163
00:18:39,708 --> 00:18:42,500
Kalau nak bantu, balik dan makan ubat.

164
00:18:43,083 --> 00:18:44,083
Han Chieh.

165
00:18:45,208 --> 00:18:49,750
Jika awak rasa pokok hajat mengarut,
buatlah hajat kepada Putera Mahkota.

166
00:18:55,333 --> 00:18:57,416
Mintalah dikurniakan kemenangan.

167
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:58,916
Okey?

168
00:19:03,250 --> 00:19:05,041
Itu bergantung pada dia.

169
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,583
Saya tak pernah merayu kepada dia.

170
00:19:10,458 --> 00:19:11,500
Lagipun,

171
00:19:13,333 --> 00:19:15,208
jika saya menyimpan harapan,

172
00:19:16,750 --> 00:19:18,583
saya lebih kecewa jika gagal.

173
00:19:39,208 --> 00:19:42,458
Pak cik buat apa? Kenapa belum pergi lagi?

174
00:19:46,875 --> 00:19:50,041
Ini rumah saya. Kenapa saya perlu pergi?

175
00:19:50,541 --> 00:19:52,708
- Kenapa tunggu di sini?
- Awak pun kenapa?

176
00:19:52,791 --> 00:19:54,583
Ejen Kayangan kena berlawan.

177
00:19:54,666 --> 00:19:58,291
Baguslah. Saya mohon jadi
ejen kayangan Dewa Guan.

178
00:19:58,375 --> 00:20:02,333
Dewa Guan dah panggil temu duga?
Jika dia tak layan, kenapa nak degil?

179
00:20:02,416 --> 00:20:04,833
Jika dia tak pergi,
saya pun tak nak juga.

180
00:20:04,916 --> 00:20:06,708
Apa kaitannya dengan awak?

181
00:20:07,416 --> 00:20:10,708
Awak mesti pergi.
Berlawan kerja orang lelaki.

182
00:20:15,666 --> 00:20:17,083
Ayam gunting.

183
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:18,875
Rusuk.

184
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:22,625
Popia goreng. Ayam gunting.

185
00:20:26,958 --> 00:20:30,750
- Saya suruh tunggu di rumah, kenapa…
- Popia… Ayam.

186
00:20:32,083 --> 00:20:33,041
Rusuk.

187
00:20:34,458 --> 00:20:35,625
Popiah.

188
00:20:36,416 --> 00:20:37,291
Ayam gunting.

189
00:20:39,708 --> 00:20:40,541
Ayam gunting.

190
00:20:40,625 --> 00:20:41,458
Rusuk…

191
00:20:46,166 --> 00:20:48,500
Tadi saya beli makanan.
Kenapa saya di sini?

192
00:21:18,583 --> 00:21:19,500
Chieh?

193
00:21:20,791 --> 00:21:23,125
- Kenapa saya balik ke sini?
- Apa jadi?

194
00:21:23,833 --> 00:21:25,583
Sebab mereka rasa bersalah?

195
00:21:26,166 --> 00:21:28,333
Tak, mereka dirasuklah.

196
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:31,541
Ini mesti kerja Wu Tien-chi.

197
00:21:32,791 --> 00:21:34,291
Apa muslihat dia?

198
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:38,000
Kita nak biar
semua orang pergi atau balik?

199
00:21:40,458 --> 00:21:41,625
Hari dah gelap.

200
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:14,833
Bangkitlah, wahai kamu semua.

201
00:22:22,875 --> 00:22:25,583
Pergilah ke Pasar Dongfeng.

202
00:22:25,666 --> 00:22:28,833
Berseronoklah dengan Han Chieh,
budak mentah itu.

203
00:22:29,458 --> 00:22:30,833
Kali ini,

204
00:22:31,458 --> 00:22:34,041
tiada sesiapa lagi boleh halang aku

205
00:22:34,125 --> 00:22:38,250
daripada mendapatkan
kuasa syaitan aku semula!

206
00:23:03,250 --> 00:23:04,666
PENGHUNI DONGFENG SAHAJA

207
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:05,583
Hati-hati.

208
00:23:07,875 --> 00:23:09,416
- Minumlah air dulu.
- Nah.

209
00:23:18,583 --> 00:23:19,416
Chieh.

210
00:23:20,666 --> 00:23:23,666
Apa yang jadi di luar? Mereka datang?

211
00:23:26,041 --> 00:23:29,500
Mereka sampai tak lama lagi.
Dia tunggu bulan terbit.

212
00:23:30,916 --> 00:23:34,333
Perang ini sampai pagi. Larat tak?

213
00:23:34,416 --> 00:23:39,375
Hei, kita satu pasukanlah.
Saya bertahan selagi awak bertahan.

214
00:23:41,041 --> 00:23:44,375
- Ada pisau dapur?
- Untuk apa? Bunuh roh?

215
00:23:44,875 --> 00:23:45,750
Ya.

216
00:23:46,708 --> 00:23:48,458
Kad saya dah tak banyak.

217
00:23:48,541 --> 00:23:51,625
Saya mesti berjimat
sebelum Raja Syaitan muncul.

218
00:23:52,416 --> 00:23:57,041
Ikat tangkal yang saya beri dulu
pada senjata. Itu membantu.

219
00:23:58,750 --> 00:24:01,291
Leafy, Kak Lo, Mei-na.

220
00:24:03,375 --> 00:24:05,625
Ambil kunci jiran-jiran.

221
00:24:05,708 --> 00:24:08,291
Pergi kumpul bekalan untuk kegunaan nanti.

222
00:24:08,375 --> 00:24:10,500
Mari kita bersedia untuk berperang!

223
00:24:41,083 --> 00:24:43,958
Kita nak perang.
Kenapa bawa patung dewa dan selimut?

224
00:24:44,041 --> 00:24:45,875
Han Chieh!

225
00:24:46,916 --> 00:24:48,250
Ada benda masuk.

226
00:27:15,375 --> 00:27:17,458
- Pistol apa itu?
- Pistol kebaikan.

227
00:27:17,541 --> 00:27:21,166
Diamlah. Pistol dan peluru kami
dah diberkati oleh Dewa Guan.

228
00:27:21,250 --> 00:27:23,500
Fu yang ajar. Kenapa tak guna kad itu?

229
00:27:23,583 --> 00:27:24,791
Kalaulah boleh guna.

230
00:27:58,666 --> 00:27:59,958
Berambus.

231
00:28:13,333 --> 00:28:14,708
Kenapa mereka pergi?

232
00:28:14,791 --> 00:28:16,416
- Mereka pergi.
- Apa jadi?

233
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:18,833
Pn. Wang. Buka pintu.

234
00:28:19,458 --> 00:28:20,666
Buka pintu sekarang.

235
00:28:20,750 --> 00:28:23,166
KALAU RAJA SYAITAN MASUK, DIA AKAN MATI

236
00:30:01,125 --> 00:30:03,833
Wu Tien-chi datang.
Kamu masuk dan jaga mereka.

237
00:30:03,916 --> 00:30:06,625
- Mujur Fu ajar kita.
- Dan Chieh buka mata ketiga saya.

238
00:30:06,708 --> 00:30:10,625
Chieh, jantung saya dah nak berhenti.
Menakutkan betul.

239
00:30:17,666 --> 00:30:18,500
Mana Leafy?

240
00:30:19,208 --> 00:30:20,208
Di mana dia?

241
00:30:24,958 --> 00:30:26,083
Kamu jaga di sini.

242
00:30:31,125 --> 00:30:32,333
Awak nampak Leafy?

243
00:30:32,833 --> 00:30:34,333
Bukankah dia dengan awak?

244
00:30:40,041 --> 00:30:41,458
Tingkat bawah.

245
00:30:47,583 --> 00:30:48,833
Masuk cepat.

246
00:31:16,958 --> 00:31:17,875
Wu Tien-chi.

247
00:31:18,375 --> 00:31:19,458
Tunggu.

248
00:31:36,875 --> 00:31:39,333
Kau fikir hantu merah dan putih
muncul di rumahnya

249
00:31:39,416 --> 00:31:42,208
sebab ibu dia jumpa
pakar feng syui lemah itu?

250
00:31:47,666 --> 00:31:49,250
Tuan Han, saya Leafy.

251
00:31:49,333 --> 00:31:51,666
Ada orang letak ini
di bawah bantal ayah saya.

252
00:31:51,750 --> 00:31:53,333
Dia dipukau hantu wanita.

253
00:31:57,666 --> 00:32:00,083
Dari awal-awal lagi, dialah bidak

254
00:32:00,833 --> 00:32:03,375
yang Raja Syaitan letak di sebelah kau.

255
00:32:05,333 --> 00:32:07,916
Aku hantar hantu ke rumahnya setiap malam

256
00:32:09,750 --> 00:32:11,291
untuk tiup tenaga syaitan

257
00:32:12,291 --> 00:32:13,583
ke dalam tubuhnya.

258
00:32:14,791 --> 00:32:17,416
Supaya hatinya menjadi hati syaitan.

259
00:32:25,833 --> 00:32:28,208
Lama kita tak jumpa, budak.

260
00:32:45,875 --> 00:32:49,208
Kau dah jauh lebih matang
berbanding beberapa tahun lalu.

261
00:32:51,875 --> 00:32:54,958
Penumbuk aku pun dah lebih kuat.
Kau nak rasa?

262
00:32:59,625 --> 00:33:05,041
Dalam ramai-ramai ejen kayangan
yang aku pernah lawan,

263
00:33:05,125 --> 00:33:09,125
cuma penumbuk kau pada muka aku
yang aku rasa paling…

264
00:33:09,875 --> 00:33:11,208
memuaskan.

265
00:33:11,291 --> 00:33:13,208
Sudah-sudahlah mengarut.

266
00:33:13,291 --> 00:33:15,333
Kau guna Chen Chi-sha sampai mati

267
00:33:15,416 --> 00:33:18,625
dan kau guna hati Leafy
untuk lahirkan pembantu baru…

268
00:33:19,333 --> 00:33:20,458
Wu Tien-chi, bukan?

269
00:33:20,541 --> 00:33:21,875
Wu Tien-chi?

270
00:33:23,708 --> 00:33:26,791
Dia memang cukup jahat,
sayangnya tak cukup berbakat.

271
00:33:26,875 --> 00:33:30,333
Rugilah jika aku beri
benda sebagus ini kepada dia, bukan?

272
00:33:37,416 --> 00:33:39,541
Aku nak beri kau hati syaitan ini.

273
00:33:41,208 --> 00:33:42,041
Aku?

274
00:33:42,125 --> 00:33:45,375
Kau muda daripada Chen Chi-sha,
handal daripada Wu Tien-chi.

275
00:33:45,458 --> 00:33:47,041
Apa salahnya?

276
00:33:50,583 --> 00:33:52,625
Aku cemburu dengan Putera Mahkota.

277
00:33:52,708 --> 00:33:55,583
Bagaimana dia jumpa
pembantu hebat macam kau?

278
00:33:56,791 --> 00:33:58,041
Kerjalah untuk aku.

279
00:33:58,708 --> 00:34:01,458
Aku takkan layan kau teruk
macam dia layan kau.

280
00:34:01,541 --> 00:34:03,916
Aku boleh beri kau apa saja.

281
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:06,958
Kau boleh pukul dan bunuh sesiapa saja.

282
00:34:11,541 --> 00:34:13,583
Tapi itu tak sama macam pukul kau.

283
00:34:14,083 --> 00:34:16,208
Makan makanan tak sama macam makan tahi.

284
00:34:16,791 --> 00:34:19,916
Jadi, kau cuma pukul orang jahatlah?

285
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:23,166
Tak, tunggu.

286
00:34:24,416 --> 00:34:26,875
Kau buat seluruh keluarga kau mati.

287
00:34:28,708 --> 00:34:31,083
Maknanya kau pun orang jahat juga.

288
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:35,875
Sebab itu aku sanggup jadi hamba dia.

289
00:34:38,416 --> 00:34:43,875
Jika kau benarkan aku
pindahkan hati syaitan kepada kau,

290
00:34:43,958 --> 00:34:46,791
kau boleh dapat kuasa syaitan yang kuat

291
00:34:47,500 --> 00:34:50,833
dan bebas sepenuhnya
daripada Putera Mahkota Ketiga.

292
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:54,416
Kau boleh jadi ejen aku

293
00:34:54,500 --> 00:34:57,416
dan menakluki ketiga-tiga alam
bersama aku.

294
00:34:57,500 --> 00:34:59,083
Celaka kau. Aku tak nak.

295
00:35:02,333 --> 00:35:04,583
Kau ingat kau ada pilihan?

296
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,666
Kau dah terlambat.

297
00:35:07,750 --> 00:35:09,833
Hati syaitan dah membesar

298
00:35:09,916 --> 00:35:13,666
dan tubuhnya boleh hancur meletup
bila-bila masa saja.

299
00:35:18,416 --> 00:35:20,666
Kau nak dia mati dengan tragik?

300
00:35:32,083 --> 00:35:35,125
Aku cuma sanggup tukar hati
dengan dua syarat.

301
00:35:36,250 --> 00:35:38,541
Jangan kacau manusia dan hantu
di Pasar Dongfeng.

302
00:35:39,708 --> 00:35:40,583
Syarat kedua.

303
00:35:44,208 --> 00:35:45,750
Beri hati aku kepada dia.

304
00:35:48,208 --> 00:35:49,333
Aku nak dia hidup.

305
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:57,041
Tapi dia dah ditakdirkan mati.
Kau tak tahukah?

306
00:35:59,250 --> 00:36:00,458
Apa maksud kau?

307
00:36:01,375 --> 00:36:04,250
Leukemianya dah lama teruk.

308
00:36:05,416 --> 00:36:06,958
Selama ini,

309
00:36:07,041 --> 00:36:11,000
dia dapat hidup pun
dengan kuasa hati syaitan.

310
00:36:15,041 --> 00:36:16,541
Dia tak beritahu kaukah?

311
00:36:20,875 --> 00:36:22,083
Selepas jatuh sakit,

312
00:36:22,166 --> 00:36:24,875
kadangkala saya datang
untuk tenangkan fikiran.

313
00:36:24,958 --> 00:36:27,666
Awak rasa dunia boleh
jadi aman dengan hajat?

314
00:36:28,625 --> 00:36:29,666
Mungkin.

315
00:36:29,750 --> 00:36:31,416
Han Chieh, senyum.

316
00:36:32,666 --> 00:36:35,833
Sebab saya tujukan
kasih sayang saya kepada dunia.

317
00:36:41,375 --> 00:36:43,375
Dapat hidup sehari lagi pun berbaloi.

318
00:36:47,041 --> 00:36:49,333
Okey, aku setuju.

319
00:36:53,708 --> 00:36:55,625
Tapi kau mesti beri hati aku kepada dia.

320
00:36:56,541 --> 00:36:58,791
Tapi aku nak pastikan dia masih hidup

321
00:36:59,666 --> 00:37:01,458
sebelum aku terima hati syaitan kau.

322
00:37:06,166 --> 00:37:08,416
Aku dah bunuh ramai orang.

323
00:37:09,625 --> 00:37:11,875
Ini kali pertama aku selamatkan orang.

324
00:37:15,208 --> 00:37:16,958
Selepas bekerja untuk aku,

325
00:37:17,041 --> 00:37:19,375
jangan cakap begini lagi dengan aku.

326
00:42:22,958 --> 00:42:24,666
Terjemahan sari kata oleh MMA

